org.vadere.simulator.models

Class MainModelBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vadere.simulator.models.MainModelBuilder

  • public class MainModelBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class encapsulates the creation of MainModel. For creation of submodels, see SubModelBuilder! The SubModelBuilder should be used in the Model.initialize(java.util.List<org.vadere.state.attributes.Attributes>, org.vadere.state.scenario.Topography, org.vadere.state.attributes.scenario.AttributesAgent, java.util.Random) method.
